{"tid":1289851,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"任正非接受法媒專訪：鴻蒙比Android速度快60%","createTime":"2019-07-06T09:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T08:09:50.000Z","uid":221827,"like":5,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8908f94636d6661dc5fefefa054eeef85d5c87","tid":1289851,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"中國電訊設備製造商華為被指危及美國國家安全而被封殺，董事長任正非再接受外國傳媒訪問。最新一期法國新聞周刊《觀點》中，任正非講述了華為5G技術發展、中美關係、中歐關係及地緣政治等問題。<br />\n<br />\n任正非在專訪中透露，華為自主研發的操作系統「鴻蒙」旨在應用於多種設備：「我們正在研發的操作系統能夠與印刷電路板、交換機、路由器、智能手機及數據中心等兼容。」<br />\n<br />\n對於鴻蒙系統，任正非表示，該系統的處理延遲少於5毫秒。它將完美地適應物聯網，還能夠應用於自動駕駛。「我們構建這個系統，為的是能夠同步連接所有對象。這就是我們走向智能社會的方式。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到鴻蒙操作系統是不是比安卓（Android）或是蘋果Mac OS X系統更快？任正非指出：「很有可能。」他更提出技術論據，根據之前的一份報告，華為的操作系統比安卓速度快60％。<br />\n<br />\n任正非也承認，在與Google和蘋果競爭，華為有一個很大的失誤：「與蘋果的操作系統或安卓相比，我們仍然缺乏良好的應用程序生態系統。」為了解決這個問題，華為已在着手研發安卓和蘋果應用商店的替代品，並試圖吸引開發者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190706/59794320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190706%2F59794320&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=87a05cfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190706%2F59794320&h=69b45d2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190706/59794320</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6e6d464adccf977c36ca7857ce25d51407dc83","tid":1289851,"uid":15984,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"有無巴打搞「愛國行動-蘋果換華為計劃」<br />\n<br />\n回收啲老人啲iPhone 換部新華為比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利串：愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持華為"},{"pid":"3947b1501b7037bee2190bc8c4dfdd5ec66eac42","tid":1289851,"uid":45914,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da9a72ff6d60307c05d812ddaa1e687b95a0fb97","tid":1289851,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"又實驗室資料"},{"pid":"081ccc75b1a147ca1f1d853cf59b7baf596f16e9","tid":1289851,"uid":55873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"期待你立即推出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef1d73aa7db412549ef5d910b5e4942d3ae95f0","tid":1289851,"uid":38761,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"放係度唔好用咪最快！"},{"pid":"52847cf6f95485a8cdfe3d666084b206007b0804","tid":1289851,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:44:46.000Z","msg":"鴻蒙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對大陸用家 冇影響. 照用."},{"pid":"694054213ae0ac1ece2d20bf8ccde94b7a334d31","tid":1289851,"uid":257459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:50:40.000Z","msg":"Google 做唔到嘅嘢華為居然做到？<br />\n快啲攞出來，唔好得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746141dc7ab3724f9608062ac3c19ff99a61ef5a","tid":1289851,"uid":119512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:31:16.000Z","msg":"冇app裝緊快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552055cec034fa9a77e4e1f2e1257efd1bcd8495","tid":1289851,"uid":18753,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"694054213ae0ac1ece2d20bf8ccde94b7a334d31","tid":1289851,"uid":257459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:50:40.000Z","msg":"Google 做唔到嘅嘢華為居然做到？<br />\n快啲攞出來